{
  "chapter": 266,
  "chapter_summary": "第十四章 谒见齐王。肖月潭为项少龙恢复原貌，分析吕不韦、田单等人对其构成的致命威胁。龙阳君前来告知试探韩闯的结果——韩闯并非出卖项少龙之人，龙阳君提议当晚乘船逃往魏国，项少龙同意。项少龙入宫谒见齐襄王，齐王以张仪典故比喻其才能，曹秋道通过齐王转交帛信约战。出宫后解子元截住项少龙，告知仲孙龙父子愿全力支持，安排项少龙与二王子田建会面。仲孙龙父子热情款待，提供剑手保护，并承诺照顾凤菲。众人商议让项少龙在比武前找借口返回秦国以避战。本章展现齐国宫廷各方势力的复杂博弈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "老兄有什么心事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我太清楚吕不韦的为人，他怎都不会让你活着回到咸阳，愈是甜言蜜语，手底下愈是狠辣。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "在现今的情况下，我也很难帮得上忙。假若一边是李园、韩闯、郭开等要对付你，另一边的吕不韦和田单又想要你的命，你的形势比前凶险百倍。只要制造点意外，例如塌屋、遭遇风浪沉船，储君很难入任何人以罪。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "至少我在临淄应是安全的，因为谁都不敢公然对我行凶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "很难说！假若田单使人通过正式挑战的方式把你杀死，政储君将很难为你报复。你的伤势如何？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "最多两三天，我可完全复原过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我不宜常来找你，否则会惹起韩闯怀疑，唉！事情的发展，令人担心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这样事情会复杂多了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "曹秋道会否碰巧是在你偷刀时刚好在那里呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "绝对不会，他亲口对我说得到有人盗刀的消息。究竟韩闯怎样说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家照计划向韩闯提出应否对付你的问题，却给他痛骂一顿。看来并不是他出卖少龙，会否是少龙忘记曾把此事告诉其他人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "韩闯会否高明至可识穿君上是在试探他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看来他并非装姿作态，这么多年朋友，他很难瞒过奴家，这事真教人摸不着头脑。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙不用担心，无论如何奴家也会站在你的一边，不若我们今晚就走，只要返回魏境，奴家自有方法送你回秦。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "但凤菲她们怎办呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要你留下一封信交给韩闯或李园，请他代你照顾她们，那无论他们心中有什么想法，均只有照你的吩咐去行事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "无论是上将军的朋友或敌人，无不对上将军佩服得五体投地。天下间若没有上将军这等人物在，会使人大感乏味。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "人生如游戏，得田相有此雅量，佩服的应属少龙才是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大家是老朋友，大王正心急要见少龙，有什么话，留待田相设宴款待少龙时再说吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiang_wang",
      "speaker_name": "齐襄王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昔日张仪作客楚国，宴会时传看当时楚人视为镇国之宝的'和氏璧'，传来传去，忽然不翼而飞，有人怀疑是张仪偷的，把他打了一顿。张仪回家时，问妻子看看他舌头还在否，说只要舌头还在，就什么都不用怕。哈……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiang_wang",
      "speaker_name": "齐襄王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "张仪凭没有被人割去的三寸不烂之舌，封侯拜相；项上将军则凭手中之剑，成了上将军，一舌一剑，可谓先后互相辉映。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiang_wang",
      "text": "大王的比喻真妙。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "田生",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不过大将军已改用自创的长匕首，弃剑不顾哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiang_wang",
      "speaker_name": "齐襄王",
      "listener": "char_tian_sheng",
      "text": "难道寡人不晓得吗？寡人已命人去把上将军的宝器取回来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiang_wang",
      "speaker_name": "齐襄王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自先王提出'尊王攘夷'，我大齐一直抱着一匡天下、和合诸侯之志。至贵国商君变法，我们齐、秦两国，隐为东、西两大国，合则有利，分则有害，其形势显而易见。今趟仲父亲临，又有上将军作客，我们更加多三分亲近，实为最大的贺礼。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_xiang_wang",
      "speaker_name": "齐襄王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "曹公说已把宝器归还上将军，还有帛信一封，请寡人转交上将军。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这是怎么一回事，上将军见过曹公吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_xiang_wang",
      "text": "承曹公看得起，约末将于寿宴后一天在稷下学宫的观星台切磋技艺，末将不胜荣幸。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢再劳远送，让末将自行离去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这几天定要找个时间大家叙叙。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄果然一表人才，不同凡响。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "解兄的消息真快。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "宫中有啥风吹草动，休想瞒得过我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "那你知否曹秋道刚向小弟下了挑战书，约定四日后子时在稷下的观星台比武，届时不准任何人在旁观战？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这怎办才好？唉！你还可以笑得出来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "大不了弃刀认输！难道他可以杀了我吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄若这么做，不怕嬴政责怪吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "兄弟自有应付之法，解兄不用担心。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不担心就是假的，曹公的剑道已到鬼神莫测的境界，不知多少名震一方的超卓剑手，对着他就像小孩碰着个壮汉，连招架之力都没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "去见仲孙龙，他要亲自向项兄请罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "仲孙龙父子得知你是项少龙后，非常兴奋，央我来求项兄一同对抗吕不韦，有项兄说几句话，二王子说不定会改变心意。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "解兄可否安排我在今天与二王子碰碰头，但这并非为他们父子，而是为解兄做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄真够朋友，就定在今晚吧！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "在公在私，我项少龙亦会为解兄和龙爷尽心尽力，所以客气话不用说了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "现在小弟立即入宫见二王子，安排今晚的宴会，在什么地方好呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "不若到玉兰楼去，会比较自然一点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "确是好地方。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "玄华精选了一批一流的剑手出来，拨给上将军使用，他们的忠诚是无可置疑的。上将军在临淄期间，他们只会听上将军的差遣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "仲孙兄想得很周到，不过此事可否明天开始？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一切听凭上将军吩咐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说师尊向上将军下了约战书，这确是令人头痛的事。待会儿玄华去谒见师尊，看可否央他收回成命。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "不必多此一举，令师决定的事，连你们大王也左右不了，小弟亦想见识曹公的绝世剑法。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "曹公平时虽和蔼可亲，但剑出鞘后从不留情，假设上将军有什么损伤，那就……唉！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "我有自保之法，龙爷不用担心。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不若我和师妹一起去见师尊，他最疼爱师妹，说不定肯破例只作为切磋玩玩了事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "真的不用你们费神，仲孙兄本身是剑手，当知剑手的心意。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军真是了得，师尊对比武这类事早心如止水，只有上将军才能令他动心，看来是上将军那把宝刀害事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "项兄太出名了，我看玄华你最好去警告麻承甲和闵廷章两个撩事斗非的人，他们若来挑战项兄，是很难拒绝的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他们若想挑战上将军，首先要过得我仲孙玄华的一关。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "让我试试刀也好，仲孙兄有心了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "难怪上将军威震咸阳，只看上将军的胸襟气魄，便知上将军刀法已达至何等高深的境界，玄华甘拜下风，有机会希望上将军也能指点玄华两招。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "仲孙兄是手痒了，还是想秤秤小弟的斤两，看是否须向尊师求他放过我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军说笑了，玄华确是诚心求教。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我仲孙龙藉此机会向上将军表明心迹，对凤菲小姐本人再不敢有非分之想。若有违此言，教我仲孙龙曝尸荒野，请上将军代为转达此意，并为我仲孙龙向大小姐致歉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "text": "小弟可能会先大小姐一步离开临淄，麻烦龙爷给小弟照顾大小姐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_long",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙龙",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事可包在我仲孙龙身上，请上将军放心。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不若项兄在与曹公比武前找个借口回秦，那一切不是立可迎刃而解吗？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不若说贵岳丈病重，那谁都不会怪上将军失约。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "过了今晚，看看和二王子谈得怎么样才说吧！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 365
    }
